  "description": "<p><strong>We are looking for passionate individuals to join our company</strong></p>\n<p><strong>Our offer:</strong></p>\n<p>For more details: O'Coffee Club - Our Story (ocoffeeclub.com)</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>——————————</p>\n<p>✨Staff benefits✨</p>\n<ul>\n  <li>5 Days Work Week (Including Sat, Sun &amp; PH)</li>\n  <li>Attractive Salary Package</li>\n  <li>Medical Benefits</li>\n  <li>Birthday Benefit</li>\n  <li>Staff Discount</li>\n  <li>Staff Meal Allowances</li>\n  <li>Career Progression</li>\n  <li>Yearly Appraisal Bonus review</li>\n  <li>Various Locations</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Responsibilities:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Responsible for smooth daily operations in café</li>\n  <li>Preparation of high quality beverages according to menu</li>\n  <li>Light kitchen duties and preparation work</li>\n  <li>Provide good customer service</li>\n  <li>Basic housekeeping</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Passion for service and F&amp;B industry</li>\n  <li>Positive work attitude and a team player</li>\n</ul>",
