    "description": "<p>COFFEE CLUB PTE LTD an ISO 9001:2000 and HACCP certified company established since 1991, takes pride in setting the standards with our mission to remain the leading café chain in Singapore offering gourmet food and coffee with excellent customer service.</p>\r\n\r\n<p> </p>\r\n\r\n<p>Coffee Club Pte Ltd opened Singapore's first gourmet coffee house at Holland Village in 1991. With its own on-site coffee roasting facilities, the outlet set a new standard for world-class coffee delivery. The result was a taste that was consistenly more flavourful and aromatic than its nearest rivals. For 21 years, customers have returned to the cosy two-storey establishment to enjoy their favourite cup.</p>\r\n\r\n<p> </p>\r\n\r\n<p>Today Coffee Club Pte Ltd has more than 20 outlets across Singapore, Malaysian and Indonesia, each united in the drive to bring customers a pleasant contemporary all-day cafe experience- one that blends friendly and distinctive service with an environment that celebrates the best in the cafe lifestyle.</p>\r\n",
